snippet: An attempt to secure power in Quebec by calling a snap election turned against the separatist Parti Québécois on Monday.
abstract: Attempt to secure power in Quebec by calling a snap election turns against the separatist Parti Quebecois as the Liberal Party, which supports remaining in Canada, emerges with a strong victory.
lead_paragraph: An attempt to secure power in Quebec by calling a snap election turned against the separatist Parti Québécois on Monday.

headline.main: Quebecers Reject Separatists, Handing Power to Liberal Party
headline.print_headline: Quebecers Reject Separatists, Handing Power to Liberal Party
